00:24:55,451 --> 00:24:57,977
The last woman
I knew before I left.

301
00:24:57,977 --> 00:25:01,259
And the first one I met.
coming back after three years!

302
00:25:01,659 --> 00:25:03,178
Isn't that great?

303
00:25:05,201 --> 00:25:06,516
Jacques!

304
00:25:07,125 --> 00:25:08,566
