305
00:25:08,857 --> 00:25:10,167
Jacques.

306
00:25:11,171 --> 00:25:13,315
Well, answer me
something!

307
00:25:14,528 --> 00:25:16,945
You're right: it is
incredibly funny!

308
00:25:17,294 --> 00:25:18,769
