to say hello,

309
00:25:18,769 --> 00:25:20,479
if you saw that
I didn't recognize you.

310
00:25:21,387 --> 00:25:23,246
Especially since I'm with Paul!

311
00:25:23,339 --> 00:25:26,387
With Paul?
- Well, yes! Yes! With Paul!

312
00:25:27,159 --> 00:25:28,989
Paul admired you so much!

313
00:25:28,989 --> 00:25:31,430
You know, I've often thought
about you. You have!

314
00:25:31,547 --> 00:25:35,092
And to meet you here,
today. is a sign for me!

315
00:25:35,207 --> 00:25:37,263
I don't believe in accidents.

316
00:25:37,417 --> 00:25:39,510
If we're meeting
now, it means, uh.

317
00:25:40,027 --> 00:25:43,743
But, uh. really. what made you
did you choose this profession?

