382
00:30:32,025 --> 00:30:35,625
I recognized it after all! - Huh, and it's still
the ring on the curtain is missing!

383
00:30:35,625 --> 00:30:38,834
Here, drink this!
It'll help you.

384
00:30:39,160 --> 00:30:40,958
What is it?
- Aspirin.

385
00:30:41,122 --> 00:30:43,729
Yeah, there's someone downstairs
looking for you. I'll go get them.

386
00:30:50,823 --> 00:30:52,642
Lorette's mom hasn't changed.....

387
00:30:52,642 --> 00:30:54,354
That's just the way it is!

388
00:30:57,521 --> 00:31:00,776
To think of it. Claire!
- So?

389
00:31:01,958 --> 00:31:03,716
Nice girl.
- О!

390
00:31:04,465 --> 00:31:06,414
That's better, guys!

391
00:31:06,531 --> 00:31:08,362
Oh, it's Kiki!

392
00:31:11,183 --> 00:31:12,585
Hey, me first!
- No!

393
00:31:12,585 --> 00:31:15,079
He's been nicer to me
nicer to me than you!

394
00:31:17,770 --> 00:31:19,402
So much for getting even with me!

395
00:31:19,402 --> 00:31:20,869
It's so good to see you!

396
00:31:20,869 --> 00:31:23,891
You still live here?
- Yes. And still in the same room.

397
00:31:23,977 --> 00:31:26,516
Oh, you're here!
You found them.

398
00:31:27,206 --> 00:31:29,143
She will not relinquish her place
on a cannonball!

