401
00:31:34,164 --> 00:31:36,293
Nothing important...
But thanks anyway!

402
00:31:37,411 --> 00:31:38,651
Oh, boy!

403
00:31:43,164 --> 00:31:44,394
You're such a slob!

404
00:31:51,163 --> 00:31:52,675
Wow, that's funny!

405
00:31:53,034 --> 00:31:56,183
Did you collect pepperoni?
