411
00:32:09,721 --> 00:32:11,359
Here you go!
- Thanks, Paul!

412
00:32:11,359 --> 00:32:13,505
Anyway, I don't owe you
I don't owe you anything, and that's fine!

413
00:32:14,417 --> 00:32:15,857
Tell me something.
- What?

414
00:32:16,186 --> 00:32:19,199
Let's go out to dinner tonight.
all three of us.

415
00:32:26,976 --> 00:32:31,087
Oh, Mr. Jacques!
What a surprise!

416
00:32:34,500 --> 00:32:37,099
That's so sweet! Especially since
