422
00:32:54,259 --> 00:32:56,397
He always wants
for something he doesn't have!

423
00:32:56,397 --> 00:32:58,664
There's still
some rooster in the wine!

424
00:32:58,664 --> 00:33:01,124
I'm telling you I don't!

425
00:33:02,466 --> 00:33:06,135
Good afternoon, Mrs. Bastide!
- Oh, Mr. Jacques!

426
00:33:06,235 --> 00:33:09,325
How wonderful!
Wait, I'll wipe my hands.

427
00:33:09,898 --> 00:33:12,095
Who have you become
in that time?

428
00:33:12,095 --> 00:33:13,993
A lover of rooster in wine....

429
00:33:15,201 --> 00:33:16,577
What are you looking for?

430
00:33:16,687 --> 00:33:18,314
Oh, this is just what I was looking for!

431
00:33:18,574 --> 00:33:19,914
Terrible!

432
00:33:20,237 --> 00:33:22,732
After all, it's not every day
every day you come back after three years!

433
00:33:22,857 --> 00:33:26,399
You know she's here?
