here all night, are we?

451
00:34:25,457 --> 00:34:27,412
Are you still
not drinking coffee? See?!

452
00:34:27,412 --> 00:34:28,798
I remember that!

453
00:34:28,798 --> 00:34:30,820
It's like you never
never left my side.

454
00:34:30,820 --> 00:34:33,327
Coffee, as usual.
