455
00:34:34,312 --> 00:34:37,475
How funny! And here I thought
you hated coffee.

456
00:34:37,864 --> 00:34:39,682
You can have dinner without me!

457
00:34:39,682 --> 00:34:41,223
We weren't expecting you!

458
00:34:41,223 --> 00:34:42,809
Come over here!

459
00:34:45,645 --> 00:34:47,613
He's overreacting...

460
00:34:48,036 --> 00:34:50,285
I am a woman after all.
- Yes, you are!

461
00:34:50,846 --> 00:34:53,391
You're not interested
how I lived after you?

462
00:34:54,847 --> 00:34:57,379
In fact, how long have we
were together? A month?

463
00:34:57,379 --> 00:34:58,787
8 days.

464
00:34:58,787 --> 00:35:01,908
No?! How much we've accomplished
we've accomplished in eight days!

465
00:35:01,908 --> 00:35:03,579
We went to a dance,

466
00:35:03,579 --> 00:35:05,743
taking pictures at the fairgrounds
near the Invalides.

467
00:35:05,743 --> 00:35:07,737
See? I didn't forget anything!

468
00:35:07,737 --> 00:35:10,452
And the night at the Merano Circus.
Remember that too?

469
00:35:10,519 --> 00:35:13,123
Of course I remember!
- Liar!

470
00:35:13,123 --> 00:35:14,809
Our feet were never there!

471
00:35:15,635 --> 00:35:17,923
And I feel like
like we've been there too.

472
00:35:18,000 --> 00:35:21,912
Since yesterday. I've been thinking
of you. incessantly!

473
00:35:22,237 --> 00:35:23,599
No, no, that's right!

474
00:35:23,599 --> 00:35:26,589
I can even think of
a lot of tiny details.

475
00:35:26,718 --> 00:35:30,948
Like how you told me
that I was, uh. like I was falling in love for the first time.

476
00:35:31,440 --> 00:35:33,254
You're the one who told me!

477
00:35:33,266 --> 00:35:34,991
I remember, as you can see!

478
00:35:35,689 --> 00:35:37,414
I hope you didn't believe me!

479
00:35:37,414 --> 00:35:40,245
But isn't the fact that I left,
without daring to say goodbye,

480
00:35:40,245 --> 00:35:43,697
