I'm very happy to see you.

482
00:35:46,906 --> 00:35:50,218
It's even better that I made you
forget about the guy who went to Dakar!

483
00:35:50,842 --> 00:35:53,077
I even deserve
respect because, uh.

484
00:35:53,794 --> 00:35:55,633
he was three
three years younger than me!

485
00:35:55,829 --> 00:35:57,204
All right, let's go!

486
00:36:06,264 --> 00:36:08,344
See you tomorrow! I'm sorry, Kiki,
you're not mad at me?

487
00:36:08,344 --> 00:36:09,686
What hard feelings?

488
00:36:09,686 --> 00:36:12,064
Paul, you stay for me!
- All right, old boy!

489
00:36:14,615 --> 00:36:16,718
I hate you!

490
00:36:16,956 --> 00:36:19,834
I'll never be able
